<div class="column two-fifths about">
<h4>About Us</h4>
<p><strong>eLearning Industry</strong> is the largest online community of professionals involved in the eLearning industry. At eLearning Industry you will find the best collection of eLearning articles, eLearning concepts, eLearning software, and eLearning resources based on the <a title="top elearning authors" href="http://elearningindustry.com/elearning-authors" target="_blank"><strong>Top eLearning Authors</strong></a>. You are more than welcome to <a title="post elearning article" href="http://elearningindustry.com/post-here" target="_blank"><strong>Post your eLearning article</strong></a>.</p>
<p><strong>eLearning Industry</strong> is designed to:</p>
<p>share the knowledge via eLearning articles, tweets, ppp, etc,</p>
<p>help instructional designers and (or) eLearning professionals to find a project or a temporary basis job,</p>
<p>to build a safe online community of professionals involved in the eLearning industry.</p>
<p><a class="button alt" title="Contact Us" href="http://elearningindustry.com/contact-us">Contact us</a></p>
</div> 
<div class="column three-fifths menus">
